{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    { "src": "public/quickscope.html", "use": "@vercel/static" }
  ],
  "routes": [
    { "src": "/", "dest": "/public/quickscope.html" },
    { "src": "/(.*)", "dest": "/public/$1" }
  ]
}
```

Save and close, then run:
```
git add .
git commit -m "Switch to PayPal, fix Vercel routing"
git push